body:
### Shiny Application Presentation
This website describes a [multiple linear regression model Shiny application](https://datasciencespm.shinyapps.io/DevelopingDataProducts/) that provides a user the capability to:  
  * Select & display predictor variables
  * Perform exploratory data analysis
  * Fit & diagnose a multiple linear regression model

### Authors and Contributors
The author for this project is @datasciencespm.
